      <div id="about" class="about_section layout_padding">
         <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
               <div class="col-md-5">
                  <h4>ABOUT TRAVELOGUE</h4>
                  <h3 style="text-transform: none !important">We Build for Your Comfort</h3>
                  <p>Travelogue is a site to know about all the tourist spots in and around your place. People can rate all the places they've visited and comment about it. You can write your own blogs and fill them up.</p>
               </div>
               <div class="col-md-6 offset-md-1">
                  <div class="full text_align_center">
                     <img class="img-responsive" src="about.png" alt="#" />
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div id="hiw" class="hiw_section layout_padding" style="background: #1a2428;">
         <div class="container">
